<i>adverb</i>: 한가로이 [한가로이], 찬찬히 [찬ː찬히], 슬렁슬렁 [슬렁슬렁] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>한가로이 [한가로이]</dt><br>
<dd>leisurely; unhurriedly</dd><br>
<dd>바쁘지 않고 여유가 있는 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Leisurely without haste.</dd><br>
<dt>찬찬히 [찬ː찬히]</dt><br>
<dd>slowly; unhurriedly</dd><br>
<dd>동작이나 태도가 급하지 않고 조금 느리게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's behavior or attitude being slightly slow without haste.</dd><br>
<dt>슬렁슬렁 [슬렁슬렁]</dt><br>
<dd>unhurriedly; without haste</dd><br>
<dd>서두르지 않고 매우 느리게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of behaving very slowly without making haste.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>